    <h2>Support</h2>
    <p>Boarding staff are not able to provide technical support for BoarderLine, please direct any requests for help to the ICT Helpdesk, either via <a href="mailto:helpdesk@ccgs.wa.edu.au">email</a>, or in person to the Futuresphere.</p>

    <p>If you are a member of boarding staff and you require admin permissions, please contact the ICT Helpdesk.</p>
